        </div>
        <input type="hidden" name="__fluent_form_embded_post_id" value="14210"><input type="hidden" id="_fluentform_3_fluentformnonce" name="_fluentform_3_fluentformnonce" value="67f6e3a8e3"><input type="hidden" name="_wp_http_referer" value="/semi-dried-tomatoes/"><div class="ff-el-group  ff-custom_html" tabindex="-1" data-name="custom_html-3_1"><h3>Want to save this recipe?</h3>
<p>Enter your email below &amp; I'll send it straight to your inbox. <em>Plus you&rsquo;ll get more great recipes and tips from me each week!</em></p></div><div data-name="ff_cn_id_1" class="ff-t-container ff-column-container ff_columns_total_2 "><div class="ff-t-cell ff-t-column-1" style="flex-basis: 74.16%;"><div class="ff-el-group"><div class="ff-el-input--content"><input type="email" name="email" id="ff_3_email" class="ff-el-form-control" placeholder="Email Address" data-name="email" aria-invalid="false" aria-required="true"></div></div></div><div class="ff-t-cell ff-t-column-2" style="flex-basis: 25.84%;"><div class="ff-el-group ff-text-left ff_submit_btn_wrapper ff_submit_btn_wrapper_custom"><button class="ff-btn ff-btn-submit ff-btn-lg ff_btn_style wpf_has_custom_css" type="submit" name="custom_submit_button-3_2" data-name="custom_submit_button-3_2" aria-label="Send It!">Send It!</button><style>form.fluent_form_3 .wpf_has_custom_css.ff-btn-submit { background-color:rgba(0, 122, 83, 1);color:#FFFFFF;border-radius:3px;min-width:100%; }form.fluent_form_3 .wpf_has_custom_css.ff-btn-submit:hover { background-color:rgba(1, 1, 1, 1);color:#FFFFFF;border-radius:0px;min-width:100%; } </style></div></div></div></fieldset></form><div id="fluentform_3_errors" class="ff-errors-in-stack ff_form_instance_3_1 ff-form-loading_errors ff_form_instance_3_1_errors"></div></div>            <script type="text/javascript">
                window.fluent_form_ff_form_instance_3_1 = {"id":"3","ajaxUrl":"https:\/\/www.heynutritionlady.com\/wp-admin\/admin-ajax.php","settings":{"layout":{"labelPlacement":"top","helpMessagePlacement":"with_label","errorMessagePlacement":"inline","asteriskPlacement":"asterisk-right"},"restrictions":{"denyEmptySubmission":{"enabled":false}}},"form_instance":"ff_form_instance_3_1","form_id_selector":"fluentform_3","rules":{"email":{"required":{"value":true,"message":"This field is required","global":false,"global_message":"This field is required"},"email":{"value":true,"message":"This field must contain a valid email","global":false,"global_message":"This field must contain a valid email"}}},"debounce_time":300};
                            </script>
            



<p>Hands down, my favourite way to use semi-dried tomatoes is as a pizza topping. These beauties are sooooooo much better than fresh tomatoes on top of a pizza because they're not wet so they don't weep out a pool of liquid when they hit the oven.</p>



<p>I make a batch of these every time we have a pizza night, and I recommend you try them on this simple <a href="https://www.heynutritionlady.com/naan-pizza-margherita-flatbread/">Naan Pizza</a>. Also, you pretty much can't beat semi-dried tomatoes as a topping on <a href="https://www.heynutritionlady.com/toast-for-dinner-herbed-ricotta-4-ways/">luxuriously simple ricotta toast</a>. </p>
</div></div>


<div class="wp-block-image">
<figure class="aligncenter"><img decoding="async" width="680" height="1020" data-pin-description="These Semi-Dried Tomatoes are amazing little flavour bombs. Oven dried tomatoes are easy to make at home, and are perfect to add to salads, sandwiches, pizza, or meal bowls. Make the most out of tomato season by freezing a big batch of semi-dried tomatoes to use down the road. #driedtomatoes #ovendried #preserves #tomatoes #vegan #heynutritionlady" src="data:image/svg+xml,%3Csvg%20xmlns='http://www.w3.org/2000/svg'%20viewBox='0%200%20680%201020'%3E%3C/svg%3E" alt="a wooden bowl of cherry tomatoes and small bowls of oil, herbs, and salt to the side" class="wp-image-14214" data-lazy-srcset="https://www.heynutritionlady.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/09/tomatoes_salt_herbs_oil-680x1020.jpg 680w, https://www.heynutritionlady.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/09/tomatoes_salt_herbs_oil-200x300.jpg 200w, https://www.heynutritionlady.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/09/tomatoes_salt_herbs_oil-768x1152.jpg 768w, https://www.heynutritionlady.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/09/tomatoes_salt_herbs_oil.jpg 1067w" data-lazy-sizes="(max-width: 680px) 100vw, 680px" data-pin-media="https://www.heynutritionlady.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/09/tomatoes_salt_herbs_oil.jpg" data-lazy-src="https://www.heynutritionlady.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/09/tomatoes_salt_herbs_oil-680x1020.jpg"><noscript><img decoding="async" width="680" height="1020" data-pin-description="These Semi-Dried Tomatoes are amazing little flavour bombs. Oven dried tomatoes are easy to make at home, and are perfect to add to salads, sandwiches, pizza, or meal bowls. Make the most out of tomato season by freezing a big batch of semi-dried tomatoes to use down the road. #driedtomatoes #ovendried #preserves #tomatoes #vegan #heynutritionlady" src="https://www.heynutritionlady.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/09/tomatoes_salt_herbs_oil-680x1020.jpg" alt="a wooden bowl of cherry tomatoes and small bowls of oil, herbs, and salt to the side" class="wp-image-14214" srcset="https://www.heynutritionlady.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/09/tomatoes_salt_herbs_oil-680x1020.jpg 680w, https://www.heynutritionlady.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/09/tomatoes_salt_herbs_oil-200x300.jpg 200w, https://www.heynutritionlady.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/09/tomatoes_salt_herbs_oil-768x1152.jpg 768w, https://www.heynutritionlady.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/09/tomatoes_salt_herbs_oil.jpg 1067w" sizes="(max-width: 680px) 100vw, 680px" data-pin-media="https://www.heynutritionlady.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/09/tomatoes_salt_herbs_oil.jpg"></noscript></figure>
</div>


<h2 class="wp-block-heading" id="h-let-s-make-semi-dried-tomatoes-together">Let's make Semi-Dried Tomatoes together!</h2>



<p>Ok, friend. You need just a handful of ingredients to get started. If you prefer to skip straight to the recipe, by all means use the "jump" button to go straight there. Otherwise, join me for a scroll and a visual walk-through.</p>



<div class="wp-block-group has-background" style="background-color:#fafafa"><div class="wp-block-group__inner-container is-layout-flow wp-block-group-is-layout-flow">
<h2 class="wp-block-heading" id="h-step-1-slice-your-maters">Step 1: slice your 'maters</h2>


<div class="wp-block-image">
<figure class="aligncenter"><img decoding="async" width="1067" height="1600" data-pin-nopin="true" data-pin-description="These Semi-Dried Tomatoes are amazing little flavour bombs. Oven dried tomatoes are easy to make at home, and are perfect to add to salads, sandwiches, pizza, or meal bowls. Make the most out of tomato season by freezing a big batch of semi-dried tomatoes to use down the road. #driedtomatoes #ovendried #preserves #tomatoes #vegan #heynutritionlady" src="data:image/svg+xml,%3Csvg%20xmlns='http://www.w3.org/2000/svg'%20viewBox='0%200%201067%201600'%3E%3C/svg%3E" alt="cherry tomatoes in a white colander and a wooden cutting board with sliced tomatoes" class="wp-image-14213" data-lazy-srcset="https://www.heynutritionlady.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/09/sliced_tomatoes.jpg 1067w, https://www.heynutritionlady.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/09/sliced_tomatoes-200x300.jpg 200w, https://www.heynutritionlady.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/09/sliced_tomatoes-768x1152.jpg 768w, https://www.heynutritionlady.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/09/sliced_tomatoes-680x1020.jpg 680w" data-lazy-sizes="(max-width: 1067px) 100vw, 1067px" data-pin-media="https://www.heynutritionlady.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/09/sliced_tomatoes.jpg" data-lazy-src="https://www.heynutritionlady.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/09/sliced_tomatoes.jpg"><noscript><img decoding="async" width="1067" height="1600" data-pin-nopin="true" data-pin-description="These Semi-Dried Tomatoes are amazing little flavour bombs. Oven dried tomatoes are easy to make at home, and are perfect to add to salads, sandwiches, pizza, or meal bowls. Make the most out of tomato season by freezing a big batch of semi-dried tomatoes to use down the road. #driedtomatoes #ovendried #preserves #tomatoes #vegan #heynutritionlady" src="https://www.heynutritionlady.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/09/sliced_tomatoes.jpg" alt="cherry tomatoes in a white colander and a wooden cutting board with sliced tomatoes" class="wp-image-14213" srcset="https://www.heynutritionlady.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/09/sliced_tomatoes.jpg 1067w, https://www.heynutritionlady.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/09/sliced_tomatoes-200x300.jpg 200w, https://www.heynutritionlady.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/09/sliced_tomatoes-768x1152.jpg 768w, https://www.heynutritionlady.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/09/sliced_tomatoes-680x1020.jpg 680w" sizes="(max-width: 1067px) 100vw, 1067px" data-pin-media="https://www.heynutritionlady.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/09/sliced_tomatoes.jpg"></noscript><figcaption class="wp-element-caption">I love using cherry tomatoes or baby plum tomatoes for this recipe. Just slice them right down the middle and we're good to go.</figcaption></figure>
</div></div></div>



<div class="wp-block-group has-background" style="background-color:#fafafa"><div class="wp-block-group__inner-container is-layout-flow wp-block-group-is-layout-flow">
<h2 class="wp-block-heading" id="h-step-2-season-em-up">Step 2: season 'em up</h2>


<div class="wp-block-image">
<figure class="aligncenter"><img decoding="async" width="1200" height="800" data-pin-nopin="true" data-pin-description="These Semi-Dried Tomatoes are amazing little flavour bombs. Oven dried tomatoes are easy to make at home, and are perfect to add to salads, sandwiches, pizza, or meal bowls. Make the most out of tomato season by freezing a big batch of semi-dried tomatoes to use down the road. #driedtomatoes #ovendried #preserves #tomatoes #vegan #heynutritionlady" src="data:image/svg+xml,%3Csvg%20xmlns='http://www.w3.org/2000/svg'%20viewBox='0%200%201200%20800'%3E%3C/svg%3E" alt="photo collage of tomatoes in a metal bowl being tossed with oil and spices" class="wp-image-14219" data-lazy-srcset="https://www.heynutritionlady.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/09/semi-dried-tomatoes-process.jpg 1200w, https://www.heynutritionlady.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/09/semi-dried-tomatoes-process-300x200.jpg 300w, https://www.heynutritionlady.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/09/semi-dried-tomatoes-process-768x512.jpg 768w, https://www.heynutritionlady.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/09/semi-dried-tomatoes-process-680x453.jpg 680w" data-lazy-sizes="(max-width: 1200px) 100vw, 1200px" data-pin-media="https://www.heynutritionlady.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/09/semi-dried-tomatoes-process.jpg" data-lazy-src="https://www.heynutritionlady.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/09/semi-dried-tomatoes-process.jpg"><noscript><img decoding="async" width="1200" height="800" data-pin-nopin="true" data-pin-description="These Semi-Dried Tomatoes are amazing little flavour bombs. Oven dried tomatoes are easy to make at home, and are perfect to add to salads, sandwiches, pizza, or meal bowls. Make the most out of tomato season by freezing a big batch of semi-dried tomatoes to use down the road. #driedtomatoes #ovendried #preserves #tomatoes #vegan #heynutritionlady" src="https://www.heynutritionlady.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/09/semi-dried-tomatoes-process.jpg" alt="photo collage of tomatoes in a metal bowl being tossed with oil and spices" class="wp-image-14219" srcset="https://www.heynutritionlady.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/09/semi-dried-tomatoes-process.jpg 1200w, https://www.heynutritionlady.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/09/semi-dried-tomatoes-process-300x200.jpg 300w, https://www.heynutritionlady.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/09/semi-dried-tomatoes-process-768x512.jpg 768w, https://www.heynutritionlady.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/09/semi-dried-tomatoes-process-680x453.jpg 680w" sizes="(max-width: 1200px) 100vw, 1200px" data-pin-media="https://www.heynutritionlady.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/09/semi-dried-tomatoes-process.jpg"></noscript><figcaption class="wp-element-caption">Place the sliced tomatoes into a bowl and toss with olive oil, herbs, and salt.&nbsp;</figcaption></figure>
</div></div></div>



<div class="wp-block-group has-background" style="background-color:#fafafa"><div class="wp-block-group__inner-container is-layout-flow wp-block-group-is-layout-flow">
<h2 class="wp-block-heading" id="h-step-3-arrange-amp-bake">Step 3: arrange &amp; bake</h2>


<div class="wp-block-image">
<figure class="aligncenter"><img decoding="async" width="1200" height="800" data-pin-nopin="true" data-pin-description="These Semi-Dried Tomatoes are amazing little flavour bombs. Oven dried tomatoes are easy to make at home, and are perfect to add to salads, sandwiches, pizza, or meal bowls. Make the most out of tomato season by freezing a big batch of semi-dried tomatoes to use down the road. #driedtomatoes #ovendried #preserves #tomatoes #vegan #heynutritionlady" src="data:image/svg+xml,%3Csvg%20xmlns='http://www.w3.org/2000/svg'%20viewBox='0%200%201200%20800'%3E%3C/svg%3E" alt="photo collage of raw and oven dried tomatoes on a parchment lined sheet pan" class="wp-image-14218" data-lazy-srcset="https://www.heynutritionlady.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/09/semi-dried-tomatoes-process-1.jpg 1200w, https://www.heynutritionlady.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/09/semi-dried-tomatoes-process-1-300x200.jpg 300w, https://www.heynutritionlady.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/09/semi-dried-tomatoes-process-1-768x512.jpg 768w, https://www.heynutritionlady.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/09/semi-dried-tomatoes-process-1-680x453.jpg 680w" data-lazy-sizes="(max-width: 1200px) 100vw, 1200px" data-pin-media="https://www.heynutritionlady.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/09/semi-dried-tomatoes-process-1.jpg" data-lazy-src="https://www.heynutritionlady.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/09/semi-dried-tomatoes-process-1.jpg"><noscript><img decoding="async" width="1200" height="800" data-pin-nopin="true" data-pin-description="These Semi-Dried Tomatoes are amazing little flavour bombs. Oven dried tomatoes are easy to make at home, and are perfect to add to salads, sandwiches, pizza, or meal bowls. Make the most out of tomato season by freezing a big batch of semi-dried tomatoes to use down the road. #driedtomatoes #ovendried #preserves #tomatoes #vegan #heynutritionlady" src="https://www.heynutritionlady.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/09/semi-dried-tomatoes-process-1.jpg" alt="photo collage of raw and oven dried tomatoes on a parchment lined sheet pan" class="wp-image-14218" srcset="https://www.heynutritionlady.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/09/semi-dried-tomatoes-process-1.jpg 1200w, https://www.heynutritionlady.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/09/semi-dried-tomatoes-process-1-300x200.jpg 300w, https://www.heynutritionlady.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/09/semi-dried-tomatoes-process-1-768x512.jpg 768w, https://www.heynutritionlady.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/09/semi-dried-tomatoes-process-1-680x453.jpg 680w" sizes="(max-width: 1200px) 100vw, 1200px" data-pin-media="https://www.heynutritionlady.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/09/semi-dried-tomatoes-process-1.jpg"></noscript><figcaption class="wp-element-caption">Arrange the tomatoes onto a parchment-lined baking sheet cut side up.&nbsp;

Toss your sheet pans into the oven and let it cook low and slow. Depending on how big your tomatoes are, this should take about an hour.</figcaption></figure>
</div></div></div>



<div class="wp-block-group has-background" style="background-color:#fafafa"><div class="wp-block-group__inner-container is-layout-flow wp-block-group-is-layout-flow">
<h2 class="wp-block-heading" id="h-step-4-cool-amp-use">Step 4: cool &amp; use!</h2>



<figure class="wp-block-image size-full"><img decoding="async" width="1067" height="1600" data-pin-description="These Semi-Dried Tomatoes are amazing little flavour bombs. Oven dried tomatoes are easy to make at home, and are perfect to add to salads, sandwiches, pizza, or meal bowls. Make the most out of tomato season by freezing a big batch of semi-dried tomatoes to use down the road. #driedtomatoes #ovendried #preserves #tomatoes #vegan #heynutritionlady" src="data:image/svg+xml,%3Csvg%20xmlns='http://www.w3.org/2000/svg'%20viewBox='0%200%201067%201600'%3E%3C/svg%3E" alt="close up photo of semi dried tomatoes on a sheet pan" class="wp-image-14212" data-lazy-srcset="https://www.heynutritionlady.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/09/semi_dried_tomatoes_3.jpg 1067w, https://www.heynutritionlady.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/09/semi_dried_tomatoes_3-200x300.jpg 200w, https://www.heynutritionlady.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/09/semi_dried_tomatoes_3-768x1152.jpg 768w, https://www.heynutritionlady.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/09/semi_dried_tomatoes_3-680x1020.jpg 680w" data-lazy-sizes="(max-width: 1067px) 100vw, 1067px" data-pin-media="https://www.heynutritionlady.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/09/semi_dried_tomatoes_3.jpg" data-lazy-src="https://www.heynutritionlady.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/09/semi_dried_tomatoes_3.jpg"><noscript><img decoding="async" width="1067" height="1600" data-pin-description="These Semi-Dried Tomatoes are amazing little flavour bombs. Oven dried tomatoes are easy to make at home, and are perfect to add to salads, sandwiches, pizza, or meal bowls. Make the most out of tomato season by freezing a big batch of semi-dried tomatoes to use down the road. #driedtomatoes #ovendried #preserves #tomatoes #vegan #heynutritionlady" src="https://www.heynutritionlady.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/09/semi_dried_tomatoes_3.jpg" alt="close up photo of semi dried tomatoes on a sheet pan" class="wp-image-14212" srcset="https://www.heynutritionlady.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/09/semi_dried_tomatoes_3.jpg 1067w, https://www.heynutritionlady.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/09/semi_dried_tomatoes_3-200x300.jpg 200w, https://www.heynutritionlady.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/09/semi_dried_tomatoes_3-768x1152.jpg 768w, https://www.heynutritionlady.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/09/semi_dried_tomatoes_3-680x1020.jpg 680w" sizes="(max-width: 1067px) 100vw, 1067px" data-pin-media="https://www.heynutritionlady.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/09/semi_dried_tomatoes_3.jpg"></noscript><figcaption class="wp-element-caption">Cool them off, and then either use them immediately or read on for storage options.</figcaption></figure>
</div></div>



<div class="wp-block-group has-background" style="background-color:#fafafa"><div class="wp-block-group__inner-container is-layout-flow wp-block-group-is-layout-flow">
<h2 class="wp-block-heading" id="h-step-5-freeze-amp-store">Step 5: freeze &amp; store</h2>


<div class="wp-block-image">
<figure class="aligncenter"><img decoding="async" width="1200" height="800" data-pin-nopin="true" data-pin-description="These Semi-Dried Tomatoes are amazing little flavour bombs. Oven dried tomatoes are easy to make at home, and are perfect to add to salads, sandwiches, pizza, or meal bowls. Make the most out of tomato season by freezing a big batch of semi-dried tomatoes to use down the road. #driedtomatoes #ovendried #preserves #tomatoes #vegan #heynutritionlady" src="data:image/svg+xml,%3Csvg%20xmlns='http://www.w3.org/2000/svg'%20viewBox='0%200%201200%20800'%3E%3C/svg%3E" alt="photo collage of frozen semi dried tomatoes" class="wp-image-14217" data-lazy-srcset="https://www.heynutritionlady.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/09/semi-dried-tomatoes-process-2.jpg 1200w, https://www.heynutritionlady.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/09/semi-dried-tomatoes-process-2-300x200.jpg 300w, https://www.heynutritionlady.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/09/semi-dried-tomatoes-process-2-768x512.jpg 768w, https://www.heynutritionlady.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/09/semi-dried-tomatoes-process-2-680x453.jpg 680w" data-lazy-sizes="(max-width: 1200px) 100vw, 1200px" data-pin-media="https://www.heynutritionlady.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/09/semi-dried-tomatoes-process-2.jpg" data-lazy-src="https://www.heynutritionlady.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/09/semi-dried-tomatoes-process-2.jpg"><noscript><img decoding="async" width="1200" height="800" data-pin-nopin="true" data-pin-description="These Semi-Dried Tomatoes are amazing little flavour bombs. Oven dried tomatoes are easy to make at home, and are perfect to add to salads, sandwiches, pizza, or meal bowls. Make the most out of tomato season by freezing a big batch of semi-dried tomatoes to use down the road. #driedtomatoes #ovendried #preserves #tomatoes #vegan #heynutritionlady" src="https://www.heynutritionlady.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/09/semi-dried-tomatoes-process-2.jpg" alt="photo collage of frozen semi dried tomatoes" class="wp-image-14217" srcset="https://www.heynutritionlady.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/09/semi-dried-tomatoes-process-2.jpg 1200w, https://www.heynutritionlady.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/09/semi-dried-tomatoes-process-2-300x200.jpg 300w, https://www.heynutritionlady.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/09/semi-dried-tomatoes-process-2-768x512.jpg 768w, https://www.heynutritionlady.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/09/semi-dried-tomatoes-process-2-680x453.jpg 680w" sizes="(max-width: 1200px) 100vw, 1200px" data-pin-media="https://www.heynutritionlady.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/09/semi-dried-tomatoes-process-2.jpg"></noscript><figcaption class="wp-element-caption">Because, unlike fully-dried tomatoes, these beauties do retain quite a bit of moisture, their shelf life is quite short. If you know you're not going to use them that quickly or you want to make a big batch, I recommend you freeze them.

To freeze your oven-dried tomatoes, place a sheet of parchment on a cookie sheet and arrange the tomatoes in a single layer. Freeze the tomatoes overnight, then transfer them to a freezer bag for long-term storage.</figcaption></figure>
</div></div></div>


