<h2 class="wprm-recipe-name wprm-block-text-bold">Semi-Dried Tomatoes (Easy Oven-Roasted Method)</h2>
<div class="wprm-spacer" style="height: 5px;"></div>
<div class="wprm-recipe-summary wprm-block-text-normal"><span style="display: block;">These <strong>semi-dried tomatoes</strong> are rich, concentrated, and bursting with sweet tomato flavor. Slowly roasted in the oven, they&rsquo;re easy to make at home and perfect for adding to salads, sandwiches, pizzas, or grain bowls. Make a double batch and freeze them for later &mdash; a simple way to enjoy peak tomato flavor all year long.</span></div>
