	<li class="comment even thread-even depth-1" id="comment-127698">
	<article id="article-comment-127698">

		
		<header class="comment-header">
			<p class="comment-author">
				<span class="comment-author-name">Loretta</span> <span class="says">says</span>			</p>

			<p class="comment-meta"><time class="comment-time">September 05, 2022 at 1:32 am</time></p>		</header>

		<div class="comment-content">
			
			<p>I just tried this recipe and it was wonderful! I have a slow oven so they took an extra 30 mins, but the result is little morsels of what I call savory candy! I can’t stop eating them! They will be glorious on a pizza!</p>
		</div>

		<div class="comment-reply"><a rel="nofollow" class="comment-reply-link" href="#comment-127698" data-commentid="127698" data-postid="14210" data-belowelement="article-comment-127698" data-respondelement="respond" data-replyto="Reply to Loretta" aria-label="Reply to Loretta">Reply</a></div>
		
	</article>
	<ul class="children">

	<li class="comment byuser comment-author-themuffinmyth bypostauthor odd alt depth-2" id="comment-127713">
	<article id="article-comment-127713">

		
		<header class="comment-header">
			<p class="comment-author">
				<span class="comment-author-name">Katie Trant</span> <span class="says">says</span>			</p>

			<p class="comment-meta"><time class="comment-time">September 06, 2022 at 7:34 am</time></p>		</header>

		<div class="comment-content">
			
			<p>These are my favourite thing to put on pizza! Glad you enjoy them as much as I do 🙂</p>
		</div>

		<div class="comment-reply"><a rel="nofollow" class="comment-reply-link" href="#comment-127713" data-commentid="127713" data-postid="14210" data-belowelement="article-comment-127713" data-respondelement="respond" data-replyto="Reply to Katie Trant" aria-label="Reply to Katie Trant">Reply</a></div>
		
